    <title>markdown语法集</title>
    <url>/2020/04/04/markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>参考链接<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/markdown/3245829?fr=aladdin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">markdown百度百科</a>，<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/ebe52d2d468f" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Markdown语法大全(超级版)</a>，<br><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/20409634/answer/90728572" target="_blank" rel="noopener">怎样引导新手使用 Markdown</a>，<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/191d1e21f7ed/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Markdown基本语法</a>，<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/280c6a6f2594" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MarkDown添加图片的三种方式</a><br><strong>1. 标题</strong><br>在标题面前加上#空格即可<br>几级标题就加几个#，敲完#要再敲个空格再写标题如下：<br><img src="./biaoti.jpg" alt="Alt text"></p>
</blockquote>
<p>效果图是这样的：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><img src="./biaotixiaoguo.png" alt="Alt text"></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>2. 引用，多级引用</strong><br>在文本面前加上&gt;空格</p>
<blockquote>
<p><img src="./yinyong.png" alt="Alt text"></p>
</blockquote>
<p>效果图：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><img src="./yinyongxiaoguo.png" alt="Alt text"></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>3. 字体</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>粗体和斜体用代码:<blockquote>
<p><code>&lt;b&gt;粗体&lt;/b&gt;</code><br><code>&lt;i&gt;斜体&lt;/i&gt;</code></p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<p>用符号：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><img src="./ziti.png" alt="Alt text"></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>注意：字体的高亮用两对等号</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p>效果：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><img src="./zitixiaoguo.png" alt="Alt text"></p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>字体的样式（字体，颜色，大小）<blockquote>
<p><code>&lt;font face=&quot;黑体&quot; color=&quot;red&quot; size=12&gt;黑体&lt;/font&gt;</code><br>这个效果图就省略咯</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>4. 有序列表，无序列表</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>有序列表就是在数字后面加上英语符号点“.”</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
  </entry>
